## 题目:输出结果？

```js
        Promise.resolve().then(()=>{
            console.log(0);
            return Promise.resolve(4);
        }).then((res)=>{
            console.log(res);
        })

        Promise.resolve().then(()=>{
            console.log(1);
        }).then(()=>{
            console.log(2);
        }).then(()=>{
            console.log(3);
        }).then(()=>{
            console.log(5);
        }).then(()=>{
            console.log(6);
        })
```

